About This Company
Norconsulting, founded in 2001, as a global recruitment consultancy, specialising in the Engineering, Telecom, Health, IT, Oil & Gas and Pharma sectors.We opened our first office in MADRID and since then we’ve kept on growing. In 2003 we expanded into European markets, initially recruiting from our UK offices.
